so]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Emily Elconin/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着伊朗战争进入第五周，特朗普的 MAGA 基础&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;出现裂痕&lt;/strong&gt;，将通常统一的保守党政治行动会议变成了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/1fog-0XoQ3L2YDi1dS0IcGJGbleddoB5JlneKl4SbzfSvAKNNTz0jOMjeXIpguwHwEt7k17IYK3-IFGloEON14kyadjefwv_nXbpG24dnyOKYc6D6PcJiAA6flkhxgRMmkwHLDKhZbtVXJkqXD-LNmJa91TwC9poPdEmnAbnpc2pwelhT-4in91U7Mo-i9jde3oDjwsKYjBF337UpnSo5713mmem4BcSqWC6arVSavnYhc_LKuCvUG6Q37kO_bw5-tSyc7tpE0y32bEjwuRpjVVMoNZlpgK13-6DLykMqnoTrjVQPAjkBQSRAPB4BuC7tSNQodVkrdz5w5E0uZbpbfcnmMIT2IOvWXT9Cs_iwCnvRduYg1m2cqjci0P-gSAEuaKPj5i4-IEZitnsIxMi1uP3DxZ1TqNdL2NbfbbARILGE9su4DANFE2UAn0P-EBbUA7D4c59RfddKkF6N3Akf5xP0AU8mxcyH-CMbceKc9GpDmSnl2047Aff6vr1VEseIRZB3q6CCMwxqp_BD3Eem0Yj1pQYwys/0Qiuv5aZnPmAeJb9GuYEV62I277dkTCM/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="关于伊朗的 MAGA 分歧蔓延到 CPAC，一些人指责以色列"&gt;关于外交政策和成本上升的辩论&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;尽管大多数共和党人仍然支持总统的行动，但&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;一些特朗普的忠实支持者&lt;/strong&gt;和保守派媒体人士&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/M5uU8w7yqi9a_cmQ_Tc8MaHQiTQ6x3Tv-pm_ZwUEs8n6URU66MuPRbHcV6hoXvrL_jvd_wLri0NfQSOjkRsdSBZblEBLMO992YGUcwaafrPCnAiaeNrXr7Nq7qZrqopx_wfGuBj3A_zcwKAsdohhFVpWzaI3ydHymvaaOjtruphCR4I0xihrINhyvXhG9wYaGGzRmwojOkFOBYU-UhbTq-en5hzZtYbd0EMZnDxOo2Mx7BIYwxFIeXodi1Haj2n8oiVnMxg6_68WA466xCxmrh7KeYQTRV8TLvCPZ4-h7geYBCIkCI4ZgRcQ1KberkBMJ7QkCX7CF-WHWS52EjyAeDEMJQps53KkrW3yoyy0jmQkRJVGwbipiHIuyeApJ3Ufu0dSyzaF-oMusi7gA7qT8TdjofgPB8O9mdIGEaJ4BsqrdmcQ_C-e5GZ2tDYp7gM4J3O6ivra7H9s25DqGa31RW3_c4--i5IjC2TnncUaIQJrmNhqvqi3Ki0Lnknpq03KqShS_HpPRyQyQKtyBCtuk_bU_y6xZTshp4ZsdQorzCG1h8pb/eZx7a9WWGIiV3qEuuH_uE