pNWODYkwrrSQgYRfjhM1nkWc9Eqbgf76gPLakg_Kh8q7BAHRJ_JqRfj6GFY4yju5qpk38u0AEsV3tC-T4XP7aamSmai2PS-tm8YTAK6WqFtKJi4B3qiGWF0xOL2Z6x1LjmfOVQKmg9OJeOp9UCU9eiSyqKSI1MVTtPievl8HyUG1yGKAtrlzlIdlqkZwy7EWoT9sxAqh0oXr7sGzZ_g8P2iRJOghmeUNXy_De4i9Vgh5CjWbI3UJYXaFEwbSfv7Pz2ZLQWhumjJtF7FnzHBrEgxRbjLlofnvkXHygniFrTyjbpmGpgsmklYF8wHGN8o6Hj9rjZ0DNl4Z2QFvEvC25JF3fSQurtlgh3d2I/pBD-6KdQ8_st6A5L9ECf-Wb2ylXzuuo0/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="曾经的世界“最受欢迎的政治家”卢拉在巴西迷失了方向"&gt;显得漂泊不定时&lt;/a&gt;，对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普与巴西的贸易战的反击也给了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/7_1aG8gWS6zEiqeLSmw8Ul-jN72rUczbgLH_VtnJuzOEXRKzeaSf5Dvsyr1z_mgRmDkPGr5vN58wvk4CsXVVYWQ_JzrKCHHc_0ZURk2mSjTIAIPTZwchmR29F4HtMW_uOqZnBub61p_5WKdxZt1H_OV0UXlM99Ixkhm6bUF4P_VqkdWFdyRiaB8-HxPXKW0bNCU52P86sto0tOxs2vUd36rLm4mfQdUs1SAC-tEXjRh5J9oi3Kh0vAQIq4dXgUGOXNershJDlWKJk6WbGIHOd3ZdJ8lDLw9SRY5-uPawKOMeCD2adnkMaKVmpMgbouW7EdcC9Zc7gptkahxW7BGk94Q9kpiqCemt1Tt8270170rbpGXPPxjiE7QsijL1HZtj2XMoi50VAGsZ-mny6z1z3t6qTe1RHk1UlrncBxi11urBnAgRJYA86N6mnnQzJU1c0orm3j4v9ZKf5VAYOKfJHcleSNa8bP9o3s4Cb8jQsl5DnI8KyY2Zpgh_gcXC8IggKb8ubmXBerRjdFQ9Hyt1/moxcdlfsDqeuejoQP2BrAHg2Wo5bRGnG/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="卢拉利用特朗普的不和，将自己塑造成巴西的捍卫者"&gt;他一个可以抓住的&lt;/a&gt;叙事。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;距离十月大选仅剩几个月，卢拉现在面临着另一场考验。这一次，回归的剧本并不那么清晰。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;民意调查显示，他一度轻松的领先优势&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/nbPP_1ErlDuRBQ4InrYjNFZ-mEB7LQ1mQ_SG7yFpDOTum1WF9iasUYFytfRzzc3dDAywUen-8aKG0OXTlfpEPlb1AqT-Ne7b-xwSHDGITGKZAyHxaP38rqhskQeHFQhjIGktB9Jwbh6X63nxvcCQk-5pvMeM5Lne8EQmIzZ2zWwwWziui7ZsnPlxuXnPORuaKFAizyMYJSS2emlWUc_QPK8QI_ZAzwhAoKUQixcvqXRk4mDdUp1ckJpQYeleYG84IvykzZZ2RNSZEsu1DvG4LDJREDpAOvFCp-aEpWN2vsD7wg7_4wt5uQJsQz6IuGSgri300xmZKVMtXP6cLKmJSWIIl7hG0RIwes4Sm3WbL-YXLuY2O2tHmGccuGThzG81a6mWIk_Tq2RFJUmXoeQG1qdhYksJPtMGnXwxZBFL9Ux8UtJzS1u6Rc7btsizxeRP_GwXdSwT4WbrU0bHLzaUn_PlO00J0iNf6ZkyvewOCXGNz9m9HJZjBApa8Kce0aRoxhjGupTJzKqKikMltQc/5cAS3S6ah0bTQEhE3kBv1AI7E0tebtIW/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="巴西选举民调显示弗拉维奥·博尔索纳罗领先卢拉"&gt;已经消失&lt;/a&gt;，他的长期竞争对手、右翼前总统雅伊尔·博索纳罗的长子弗拉维奥·博尔索纳罗(Flávio Bolsonaro)小幅领先。这一逆转发生之际，选民对巴西的经济前景变得更加悲观，而大规模的腐败调查虽然没有直接牵连卢拉，但却拖累了与他关系密切的机构。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFAmrvl4AfPU/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFAmrvl4AfPU/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;卢拉已经看到了丑闻可能造成的损害。十多年前，“洗车行动”导致他精心挑选的继任者迪尔玛·罗塞夫垮台。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;政府内部对于如何应对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/SGOMn5v-ppZToB-z9LCg1NXMZDu_ghhR9KKZ-hJ6iOqwMfvGuPlJy2b5adqD5Kmgq-tEVmu49Haqo3g4EQVeWuksNJqOsfDfTld1hXtJSsa4posVdVSJaQS3eksB9nww9VYVE6QFeYCdmn9wYq_qcKY45XmW7GGDOW0bDWxr8LervoxgCmXdLfA5XZpEoedJuQdg8e5DnRiEoWoDHvmehgoMz-uyytoJhgej75UTz0slEZB5ZlNFwMi2PwvCdBxrGHL1sb3iFmalLRLR9m6Fdmq_eYv_X-C0wr_FIiHRAVB49Na6eGf4JVUIOKXhzJjW0dLwf3TxiTalhCxMT5az-LuEsj8a4OI-dChwHyyij0cFQwFPyMZwYVrtrNs0vB63_YaBeuhUnhVvPy40bdH28oR5ZmRScvyXEqp_W9m4IgtH_dV206rp9jjZCIYerJgv0Co5Rtl1TT0JnDMICAPcJha2btsoEak9mks-eejif2vG78rm6FjZsoSJRa4nf4Ck5RWgJ0jKBtSdpXLnYIk/S1Wv3BObRL-QQhdD573TP09GxTZteQ_-/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="卢拉在激烈的巴西竞选中努力阻止博尔索纳罗的崛起"&gt;几乎没有达成共识&lt;/a&gt;。一些盟友主张保持耐心，认为卢拉的经验最终会占上风。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; 